high_descs: Walk forward and turn left and go to the garbage bin on the floor by the counter.
Pick up the potato from the garbage bin.
Turn right, walk to the counter and turn right and go to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, put the potato on the top shelf for a few seconds, then take it out and close the refrigerator.
Turn around and walk back to the garbage bin.
Put the potato back in the garbage bin.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled potato in a garbage bin.

high_descs: Walk forward to the trash can.
Take the potato out of the trash can.
Turn right, walk to the sink and turn right again to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the potato in for a bit and then take it back out.
Turn around and go back to the trash can.
Put the potato back in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Chill the potato in the fridge and then take it back to the trash.

high_descs: Take a step towards the stove and turn left. Walk halfway up the counter and turn right to face the trash can.
Take the potato out of the trash can.
Turn to the right and then around to the counter behind you. Turn left and walk towards the counter. Face right and walk towards the fridge.
Place the potato on the shelf inside the fridge, shut the door and take the potato back out.
Turn around and walk to the stove. Turn left and walk to the end of the counter and face right.
Put the potato back in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: To put the potato in the fridge back to the trash can.
